@startuml pipeline-dependabot

skinparam defaultFontName Liberation Sans
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white

skinparam activity {
  BorderColor #003087
  BackgroundColor #EEF3FA
  FontColor #003087
  StartColor #003087
  EndColor #003087
  BarColor #003087
}

skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF9E6
  BorderColor #C8A400
  FontColor #555555
}

skinparam arrow {
  Color #333333
  FontColor #555555
  FontSize 9
}

note
  dependabot.yml · Triggers: weekly (Monday) for all three ecosystems
  Maximum 5 open PRs per ecosystem; minor + patch updates are grouped into one PR.
end note

|pip (requirements.txt)|
start
:Scan Python dependencies\nfor outdated versions;
:Group minor + patch updates\ninto one PR;
:Open PR targeting main\n(max 5 open PRs);
:CI workflow triggered on PR;
stop

|GitHub Actions (.github/workflows)|
start
:Scan action versions\nfor outdated pinned refs;
:Open PR per major update\nor grouped minor/patch PR;
:CI workflow triggered on PR;
stop

|Docker (Dockerfile)|
start
:Scan base image tags\nfor newer versions;
:Open PR targeting main\n(max 5 open PRs);
:CI workflow triggered on PR;
stop

@enduml
